an use, but fell out of use in the 15th century. It was reintroduced into the English-speaking world from Germany in the 19th century, but has once again gone out of fashion."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Bertha von Krenkingen was born about 1135, in Fribourg, Switzerland as the daughter of Konrad von Krenkingen and MRS Konrad von KRENKINGEN. She had at least 1 son with Liutold von Regensberg III. She died in her hometown."},"et":{"um 1135–":"umbes 1135–Surnud","1130–1202":"1130–1202","1135–Female":"1135–Surnud","1130–1168":"1130–1168","1140–1218":"1140–1218","1105–1163":"1105–1163","–Female":"Surnud","1105":"1105","1202":"1202","1168":"1168","1135":"1135","um 1135":"umbes 1135","1163":"1163","1130":"1130","1140":"1140","1218":"1218","Pays, Freiburg, Schweiz":"Freiburg, Šveits","Regensberg, Forchheim, Bayern, Germany":"Regensberg, Kunreuth, Landkreis Forchheim, Bayern, Saksamaa"},"fi":{"um 1135–":"noin 1135–Kuollut","1130–1202":"1130–1202","1135–Female":"1135–Kuollut","1130–1168":"1130–1168","1140–1218":"1140–1218","1105–1163":"1105–1163","–Female":"Kuollut","1105":"1105","1202":"1202","1168":"1168","1135":"1135","um 1135":"noin 1135","1163":"1163","1130":"1130","1140":"1140","1218":"1218","Pays, Freiburg, Schweiz":"Freiburg, Sveitsi","Regensberg, Forchheim, Bayern, Germany":"Regensberg, Kunreuth, Landkreis Forchheim, Bayern, Saksa"},"fr":{"um 1135–":"environ 1135–Décédée","1130–1202":"1130–1202","1135–Female":"1135–Décédée","1130–1168":"1130–1168","1140–1218":"1140–1218","1105–1163":"1105–1163","–Female":"Décédée","1105":"1105","1202":"1202","1168":"1168","1135":"1135","um 1135":"environ 1135","1163":"1163","1130":"1130","1140":"1140","1218":"1218","Pays, Freiburg, Schweiz":"Fribourg, Suisse","Regensberg, Forchheim, Bayern, Germany":"Regensberg, Kunreuth, Landkreis Forchheim, Bayern, Allemagne","lifeSummary":"Bertha von Krenkingen est née environ 1135, à Fribourg, Suisse, fille de Konrad von Krenkingen et MRS Konrad von KRENKINGEN. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec